AND IS THE COUSIN

24:30.235 --> 24:33.472
OF THE PALESTINIAN TEEN WHO WAS
APPARENTLY BURNED ALIVE

24:33.539 --> 24:36.508
IN WHAT MAY HAVE BEEN A REVENGE
ATTACK FOR THE MURDER

24:36.575 --> 24:39.078
OF THREE ISRAELI TEENAGERS.

